Ubuntu:
- dependencies firefox-dev
  apt-get install firefox-dev
  if ubuntu is natty, please add one line below to /etc/apt/source.list
  deb http://security.ubuntu.com/ubuntu natty-security main 
  then, sudo apt-get update, then sudo apt-get install firefox-dev.
  
- build steps:
  make

Windows VC++:
- please refer to win/httpp/httpp.vcxproj
- please build UDT source file and firefox-httpp extension file together

Fennec:
- please refer to fennec directory to build HTTPP extension for firefox-mobile 
- 
